  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7337986/" class="title-link">不一样的二战史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7337986"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kenheart_ccxuan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u64970285-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kenheart_ccxuan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">cc_剑心_心太</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-01-12"
      class="main-meta">2015-01-12 12:44:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7337986_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  历史并不只有一种表述方式，我们接受的教育似乎总是欠缺一点什么，多读读不同人笔下的历史，才能有更加全面的认识，从而做出自己的理解和判断。总的来说是一本很不错的二战史，有一些新视角，能看到战争的不同方面，喜欢军事和历史的朋友不容错过～

